<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8033345>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Thysanozoon brocchii a Dorsal view. Scale bar = 1mm. b Anterior dorsal region showing marginal tentacular eyes te. Scale bar=200µ. c Ventral view in fixed specimen showing the mouth m, the two male gonopores mg, the female gonopre fg and the developed sucker s. Scale bar = 100µ. d Section through the elongated seminal vesicle sv. Scale bar = 100µ. e Section through ovary ov. Scale bar =100µ." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8033345/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

